.TH NYXUS-DOCTOR 1 "May 2026" "NYXUS 2026.05" "NYXUS Manual"
.SH NAME
nyxus-doctor \- diagnose and repair NYXUS installation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nyxus-doctor
[\-\-fix] [\-\-verbose]
